How to Download Vizlib Library 7

How to Download Vizlib Library

  • Click on https://home.vizlib.com/vizlib-library-for-qlik-sense/#hs-chat-open

  • Click on download free trail
  • Enter your details and click on continue

  • Enter company details and then click on continue

  • Create password, check the box, and click on create account


  • Go to your email and click on the email from Vizlib. Click on “Download Vizlib Now”. This will open a new tab in your browser. Sign in to your Vizlib portal using the username and password you created earlier.

  • Click on Library after you log in and download the Vizlib library package


 


  • Go to the location of the downloaded file and copy it.

  • When you downloaded Qlik Sense Desktop, Qlik Automatically created a folder in your computer. Click on Qlik folder then click on the Sense folder. Open extensions and paste the zip file you downloaded. 


  • Unzip the file and extract it.


  • Here is a list of all the files you downloaded. Close Vizlib and log into Qlik Sense.


 

Vizlib Collaboration for Qlik Sense
